</taxonomicName>
by its combination of salmon basidioma, large angular pores (1 
<emphasis box="[1243,1267,356,377]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="177">–3</emphasis>
per mm) and small ellipsoid spores.
</paragraph>
